metadata.name: X
metadata.description:
In your eyes, I see a light  
That shines so bright and true  
Without you, I would wander through the night  
Lost and found, but never with you

Here I stand, with you in my sight  
A love that will never fade  
Lost and found, I lose if I lose you

Love cannot be bought with gold, or sold for all its worth  
It's a treasure beyond compare, a gift from heaven to earth  
Its value cannot be measured, in terms of money or fame  
For love is the most precious thing, a priceless, endless flame  
Is there a price on love? 

XOXO
